            "heading": "Support Treatment Adherence During Prescription Acne Therapy",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_jjgEEM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Isorepair range is specifically formulated to support patients undergoing prescription acne treatment, including oral isotretinoin. Developed with ceramides and biomimetic lipids to help restore barrier integrity, alongside hydrating ingredients including hyaluronic acid, Pentavitin® and glycerine, Isorepair provides clinically proven hydration support, helping to reduce transepidermal water loss (TEWL) by 46%<sup>5</sup> and maintain long-lasting skin hydration.</p><p>The range also contains niacinamide, panthenol and bisabolol to help calm sensitivity and reduce redness, supporting improved skin comfort and helping to minimise the dryness, flaking, tightness and irritation commonly associated with retinoid-based therapies.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_C6H6TB": {
