        "text_4kWHeL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>BIRETIX Tri-Active Anti-Blemish Gel combines exfoliating, sebum-regulating and skin-renewing ingredients to target multiple factors associated with blemish-prone skin. The triple-action formulation helps reduce imperfections, blemishes, excess oil and shine, while improving overall skin texture and promoting a more even-looking complexion.<sup>1</sup></p> \n\n<p>After just 28 days of use, BIRETIX Tri-Active Anti-Blemish Gel was shown to significantly reduce imperfections by 61% and blemishes by up to 76%.<sup>1,2</sup></p>",
